              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "D-T"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The solid tritium-titanium (T-Ti) target was",
                "used with 2.4 mg/cm2 in thickness and with a effective",
                "deuteron beam of 121 keV and beam current of 300 uA.",
                "Neutron energies in the measurements were determined",
                "by cross section ratios for 93Nb(n,2n)92mNb and",
                "90Zr(n,2n)89m+gZr reactions."
              ]
            }
          ],
